parameters:
So we're going to perform a ritual here... I
wonder what kind of ritual would make Dorothea so
scared...

Rosia, she said she's ready, but where is she? As
for the sacrifice...

Konoha-san, the ritual involves sucking human
blood. Dorothea-sama is a vampire after all.

The one who has their blood sucked will fall into
eternal sleep. Yes, we must offer someone as a
sacrifice.

I... It was too difficult for me... I couldn't do
it... However...

Wait... So if we don't offer a sacrifice, Dorothea
won't regain her power...?!

I see, I see~ So that's how it is~ That's good,
that's good~

Now, if only we can easily take control of this
Blood Moon Castle. It's just perfect, isn't it?
Wha... The Four Heavenly Demon Kings...?!

Demon Lord Sata, you're in a good mood. It's been
a while, Dorothea. To meet you in a place like
this... Oh my, is this also fate?
Are you trying to interrupt the ritual?!

\c[10]Demon Lord Sata\c[0], that is correct. It
would have been better if the barrier had weakened
a little more, but it seems that the ritual is
about to begin. I have come to stop it, as
expected.

You... How dare you intrude upon our sacred altar,
Sata.

Demon Lord Sata, of course I have no intention of
asking for your forgiveness. Well well, it's time
for all the nuisances to disappear~

\c[10]Demon Lord Sata\c[0] Oh...? You're the
magical girl that was mentioned in the warning...
I see, you're definitely not ordinary... It seems
like I need to get rid of you first.
◆◆◆◆◆◆「かかってきなさい」「軽くひねってあげるわ」◆◆◆◆◆◆

Rosia, Dorothea, please leave this one to me. I
will defeat them.

\c[10]Defeat Demon Lord Sata...? Did you say
you'll defeat me...? How delightful~

\c[10]Demon Lord Sata\c[0], just imagining your
confident face contorting makes my heart dance!
Now, let me make you regret it!

\c[10]Demon Lord Sata\c[0] G-geeeh...! No way...
th-this... me...

What a shame. I couldn't see my twisted face, but
being able to see your twisted face is the best.
Goodbye.

Amazing... I've never seen a magical girl who can
defeat those Four Heavenly Kings.

Well then, I suppose we have to finish the
ritual...

Yes, that's right. We were just thinking about the
ritual... Rosia, what on earth...

Dorothea-sama, here is Rosia, who wishes to return
to your blood and soul.

Wh-what are you saying! You are an important force
in battle! I can't...!

I deeply admire you, Lady Dorothea... I have
always had you in my heart. That is why, please,
make me a part of your power!

......Ugh... Is it really... okay like this... Are
you sure there won't be any regrets...

Indeed... I have been able to fulfill my duty of
protecting the Blood Moon for many years and have
enjoyed my time with Lady Dorothea. If I can now
become a part of Lady Dorothea's power... there is
nothing more I could desire.

I understand... Rosia, I will accept your
feelings. I never expected that you would think of
me... There is nothing more joyful than this.

......Ah... I love you... Lady Dorothea... I love
you so much...

\c[10]Demon Lord Sata\c[0] Hahahaha! Weak... weak!
I heard you were quite dangerous, but you're
nothing at all...

\c[10]Demon Lord Sata\c[0], it's already
impossible for you alone. Come on, give up.

\C[3]Konoha, who had been defeated, the Blood Moon
Castle was quickly taken over by the demons.
